"type":70,"value":97},"簡單說呢，就是讓處理器在沒事做的時候維持低頻率，有事做的時候變為高頻率但卻又不超過安全值。",{"type":64,"tag":93,"props":99,"children":100},{},[101],{"type":70,"value":102},"因為 CPU 頻率決定了特定時間內能夠吞吐的工作量，CPU 工作時的頻率越高，發熱量也越大，所以網路上就會出現關閉 Intel Turbo Boost 讓 CPU 不論有沒有事做都維持在基本頻率，以降低消耗電量以及發熱度的作法，雖然通常是在筆電上設定，但若想要桌機不要那麼熱情（？），也是可以設定的。",{"type":64,"tag":104,"props":105,"children":106},"article-note",{},[107,109],{"type":70,"value":108},"\n關於 Intel Turbo Boost 可參考\n",{"type":64,"tag":110,"props":111,"children":115},"a",{"href":112,"rel":113},"https://www.intel.com.tw/content/www/tw/zh/gaming/resources/turbo-boost.html",[114],"nofollow",[116],{"type":70,"value":117},"官方說明",{"type":64,"tag":119,"props":120,"children":122},"h3",{"id":121},"關閉的方式",[123],{"type":70,"value":121},{"type":64,"tag":93,"props":125,"children":126},{},[127],{"type":70,"value":128},"在我所查到的資料裡， Fedora 38 中有兩種關閉 Intel Turbo Boost 的方式。一個是透過別人寫的 GNOME 擴充套件，一個則是直接修改設定值並把他設定成開機時自動關閉。",{"type":64,"tag":93,"props":130,"children":131},{},[132],{"type":70,"value":133},"自己比較喜歡後者，因為前者須依靠別人更新的 GNOME 擴充套件，在迭代速度較快的 Fedora 中，常常升上新版本之後 GNOME 也會跟著升級，然後導致比較少見的擴充套件掛掉。但前者設定相對容易也不需要輸入什麼指令，大家可以自己挑自己喜歡的。",{"type":64,"tag":82,"props":135,"children":136},{},[],{"type":64,"tag":86,"props":138,"children":140},{"id":139},"透過-gnome-擴充套件關閉",[141],{"type":70,"value":142},"透過 GNOME 擴充套件關閉",{"type":64,"tag":93,"props":144,"children":145},{},[146,148,155],{"type":70,"value":147},"第一個方式就是透過",{"type":64,"tag":110,"props":149,"children":152},{"href":150,"rel":151},"https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/1082/cpufreq/",[114],[153],{"type":70,"value":154},"cpufreq",{"type":70,"value":156},"這個擴充套件來完成，這個套件甚至可以調整 CPU 的最低／最高頻率以及可使用的 CPU 核心數量。",{"type":64,"tag":158,"props":159,"children":161},"article-img",{"img":160},"922/5do1r7.png",[],{"type":64,"tag":93,"props":163,"children":164},{},[165,167,174],{"type":70,"value":166},"但這個套件不在 Fedora 官方套件庫內，要從",{"type":64,"tag":110,"props":168,"children":171},{"href":169,"rel":170},"https://extensions.gnome.org/",[114],[172],{"type":70,"value":173},"GNOMe Extensions 網站",{"type":70,"value":175},"自行安裝。安裝後在頂端列將「Turbo Boost」這個選項關閉就可以了。",{"type":64,"tag":82,"props":177,"children":178},{},[],{"type":64,"tag":86,"props":180,"children":182},{"id":181},"透過修改系統設定值關閉",[183],{"type":70,"value":181},{"type":64,"tag":93,"props":185,"children":186},{},[187],{"type":70,"value":188},"第二個方式就是我採用的方式了，自行修改設定值並設定為開機時自動開啟。首先建立一個 system service 檔案，可使用自己喜歡的文字編輯器：",{"type":64,"tag":190,"props":191,"children":195},"pre",{"className":192,"code":193,"language":194,"meta":49,"style":49},"language-bash shiki shiki-themes github-dark","# 建立一個system service\nsudo gnome-text-editor /etc/systemd/system/disable-intel-turboboost.service\n","bash",[196],{"type":64,"tag":197,"props":198,"children":199},"code",{"__ignoreMap":49},[200,212],{"type":64,"tag":201,"props":202,"children":205},"span",{"class":203,"line":204},"line",1,[206],{"type":64,"tag":201,"props":207,"children":209},{"style":208},"--shiki-default:#6A737D",[210],{"type":70,"value":211},"# 建立一個system service\n",{"type":64,"tag":201,"props":213,"children":215},{"class":203,"line":214},2,[216,222,228],{"type":64,"tag":201,"props":217,"children":219},{"style":218},"--shiki-default:#B392F0",[220],{"type":70,"value":221},"sudo",{"type":64,"tag":201,"props":223,"children":225},{"style":224},"--shiki-default:#9ECBFF",[226],{"type":70,"value":227}," gnome-text-editor",{"type":64,"tag":201,"props":229,"children":230},{"style":224},[231],{"type":70,"value":232}," /etc/systemd/system/disable-intel-turboboost.service\n",{"type":64,"tag":93,"props":234,"children":235},{},[236],{"type":70,"value":237},"接著貼上如下的內容：",{"type":64,"tag":190,"props":239,"children":244},{"className":240,"code":241,"filename":242,"language":243,"meta":49,"style":49},"language-ini shiki shiki-themes github-dark","[Unit]\nDescription=Disable Intel Turbo Boost using pstate driver\n\n[Service]\nExecStart=/bin/sh -c \"/usr/bin/echo 1 > /sys/devices/system/cpu/intel_pstate/no_turbo\"\nExecStop=/bin/sh -c \"/usr/bin/e